T1  - Comment: Organizations Do Not Cognize
AU  - James, Lawrence R.
AU  - Joyce, William F.
AU  - Slocum, John W.
Y1  - 1988/01/01
PY  - 1988
DA  - 1988/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1988.4306808
